        ],
        "params": {
          "text": "# \ud83d\uddfa UK Population Map (geopandas)\n\nSimplified Eurostat region boundaries are **embedded in the UK Region Boundaries node** \u2014 no shapefile, no download.\n\n- The stock **Join** node merges populations straight onto the GeoDataFrame\n- **Choropleth** = matplotlib figure card with margin callouts\n- **Interactive UK Map** = folium/Leaflet in a web view (tiles need network)\n\nNeeds `geopandas` and `folium`: Tools > Manage Packages.",
          "width": 560,
          "height": 0
        },
        "code": null,
        "label": null
      },
      {
